        <section id="description">
            <title>Description</title>
            <p class="tagDescription">Enclosed inside a &lt;mak:criterion&gt;, generates an input for that criterion. This tag is based on the &lt;mak:input/&gt; tag, and provides additionally the following attributes:</p>
        </section>
